  "text": "The main goal of clustering is to find groups of similar instances by using a set of attributes. The approach is extended by multi-view [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] and multi-layer clustering [CITATION_3] to find groups of instances that are strongly connected across multiple views. However, clustering approaches do not provide understandable and concise descriptions of these groups which are often complex and hard to find.",
